Class Grade

public class Grade extends Object

      public Grade(char mark, String subject, int studentId, Date gradeDate, String comment, int teacherId)
      Constructor for creating a new grade record.
      Parameters:
      mark - The letter grade (A-F)
      subject - The subject for which the grade was given
      studentId - The ID of the student who received the grade
      gradeDate - The date when the grade was recorded
      comment - Additional comments about the grade
      teacherId - The ID of the teacher who gave the grade
